Interface ICourse

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdvancedJavaCourse, Course, IntroJavaCourse, IntroToProgrammingCourse
    public interface ICourse
    Interface to provide methods for implementation by the abstract Course subclass, and by extension the specific Course types. The responsibility of this class is simply to define the methods needing to be implemented.
